<!DOCTYPE html>
<html lang="pt">

<head>
  <meta charset="UTF-8">
  <title>Bytebite Pizzeria</title>
  <link rel="stylesheet" href="styles.css">
  <link href="https://cdn.jsdelivr.net/npm/bootstrap@5.3.8/dist/css/bootstrap.min.css" rel="stylesheet" integrity="sha384-sRIl4kxILFvY47J16cr9ZwB07vP4J8+LH7qKQnuqkuIAvNWLzeN8tE5YBujZqJLB" crossorigin="anonymous">

</head>

<body>
  <section class="hero">
    <div class="hero-overlay"></div>

    <div class="hero-content">
      
      <h1>A sua espera</h1>
      <p>
        Massa esticada à mão, tomate San Marzano e fior di latte —
cozidos durante 90 segundos no nosso forno Stefano Ferrara a 485 °C.
      </p>
    </div>
  </section>

  
  <section class="booking">
    <div class="booking-card">
      <div class="top-bar"></div>

      <h2>Reservation Details</h2>
      <p class="subtitle">
        Escolha a data, a hora e o número de pessoas do seu grupo. A confirmação será enviada por e-mail no prazo de cinco minutos.
      </p>

      
      <form class="form">
        <input type="date" required>
        <input type="time" required>
        <input type="number" placeholder="Número de pessoas" min="1" required>
        <button type="submit">Reservar</button>
      </form>
    </div>
  </section>

  
  <section class="features">
    <div class="container">
      <h2>Porque ByteBite</h2>

      <div class="grid">
        <div class="card">
          <span>🔥</span>
          <h3>Forno a Lenha</h3>
          <p>Forno Importado de Italia.</p>
        </div>

        <div class="card">
          <span>🧀</span>
          <h3>DOP Ingredientes</h3>
          <p>Mozzarela de Italia, Azeite Portugues e Muito amor.</p>
        </div>

        <div class="card">
          <span>🍷</span>
          <h3>Aberto </h3>
          <p>Aberto de 3feira a Sabado das 18-23.</p>
        </div>
      </div>
    </div>
  </section>

  
  
  <script src="https://cdn.jsdelivr.net/npm/bootstrap@5.3.8/dist/js/bootstrap.bundle.min.js" integrity="sha384-FKyoEForCGlyvwx9Hj09JcYn3nv7wiPVlz7YYwJrWVcXK/BmnVDxM+D2scQbITxI" crossorigin="anonymous"></script>
</body>
</html>



CSS



* {
  margin: 0;
  padding: 0;
  box-sizing: border-box;
}

/* CORES */
:root {
  --primary: #C0392B;
  --secondary: #27AE60;
  --bg: #F8F1E9;
  --text: #2C3E50;
}

/* BODY */
body {
  font-family: Arial, sans-serif;
  background-color: var(--bg);
  color: var(--text);
}

/* HEADER */
.header {
  background: white;
  padding: 40px 0;
  border-bottom: 2px solid #eee;
}

.header-content {
  display: flex;
  justify-content: space-between;
  align-items: center;
}

.logo {
  color: var(--primary);
  font-weight: bold;
}

.nav span {
  margin-left: 20px;
  cursor: pointer;
  transition: 0.3s;
}

.nav span:hover {
  color: var(--secondary);
}

.nav .active {
  color: var(--primary);
  font-weight: bold;
}


.hero {
  position: relative;
  height: 80vh;
  background: url('Imagens/logo.png') center center / contain no-repeat;
  background-color: #F8F1E9; 
  display: flex;
  justify-content: center;
  align-items: center;
  text-align: center;
  color: white;
}

.hero-overlay {
  position: absolute;
  width: 100%;
  height: 80%;
  background: rgba(0,0,0,0.4);
}

.hero-content {
  position: relative;
  max-width: 600px;
  z-index: 2;
}

.hero h1 {
  font-size: 50px;
  margin: 20px 0;
  text-shadow: 2px 2px 10px rgba(0,0,0,0.7);
}

.hero p {
  text-shadow: 1px 1px 8px rgba(0,0,0,0.7);
}
.badge {
  background: var(--primary);
  padding: 5px 10px;
  border-radius: 5px;
}


.booking {
  display: flex;
  justify-content: center;
  margin-top: -80px;
  padding: 40px 20px;
}

.booking-card {
  background: white;
  padding: 30px;
  border-radius: 15px;
  width: 400px;
  box-shadow: 0 10px 30px rgba(0,0,0,0.1);
  text-align: center;
}

.top-bar {
  height: 5px;
  background: var(--primary);
  border-radius: 10px 10px 0 0;
  margin-bottom: 20px;
}

.subtitle {
  font-size: 14px;
  margin-bottom: 20px;
}


.form input {
  width: 100%;
  padding: 12px;
  margin-bottom: 15px;
  border: 1px solid #ddd;
  border-radius: 8px;
  transition: 0.3s;
}

.form input:focus {
  border-color: var(--secondary);
}


.form button {
  width: 100%;
  padding: 12px;
  background: var(--primary);
  color: white;
  border: none;
  border-radius: 8px;
  font-weight: bold;
  cursor: pointer;
  transition: 0.3s;
}

.form button:hover {
  background: var(--secondary);
}

/* FEATURES */
.features {
  padding: 60px 20px;
  text-align: center;
}

.features h2 {
  margin-bottom: 40px;
}

.grid {
  display: flex;
  gap: 20px;
  justify-content: center;
  flex-wrap: wrap;
}

.card {
  background: white;
  padding: 20px;
  border-radius: 10px;
  width: 250px;
  box-shadow: 0 5px 15px rgba(0,0,0,0.05);
  transition: 0.3s;
}

.card:hover {
  transform: translateY(-5px);
}

.card span {
  font-size: 30px;
}

.card h3 {
  margin: 10px 0;
  color: var(--primary);
}




